  {%- comment -%} Parent Brand Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-parent section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-parent__grid">
        <div class="about-parent__content">
          <span class="about-parent__label">The Parent Brand</span>
          <h2 class="about-parent__title">Born from 25 Years of Pharmaceutical Excellence</h2>
          <div class="about-parent__text rte">
            <p><strong>PRM Pharmaceuticals</strong> was founded in <strong>1999</strong> in Bhavnagar, Gujarat by <strong>Mr. Hemang Soni</strong>, a first-generation entrepreneur who set out with a single conviction — that quality Indian medicine should be affordable and accessible to every family. The company's very first product, <strong>Corylplus™</strong>, launched the same year, became the foundation stone for what would grow into one of India's respected mid-size pharmaceutical houses.</p>
            <p>Today, PRM Pharma is the <strong>largest player in the Pharma O.T.C. segment</strong> with three decades of market presence — <strong>85+ brands</strong>, <strong>250+ formulations</strong>, <strong>35,000+ satisfied customers</strong>, and a distribution network covering <strong>300+ channels across 28+ Indian states</strong> and <strong>3 international markets</strong>.</p>
            <p>In <strong>2013</strong>, recognising a growing demand for authentic, safety-tested Ayurvedic medicines, PRM Pharmaceuticals launched its Ayurveda and herbal wellness division — <strong>HerboVilla</strong>. The mission was clear: combine the wisdom of <em>ancient Ayurveda</em> with the discipline of <em>modern therapeutics</em>. We call this <strong>"SampurnaSudhha"</strong> — Pure Quality — formulations crafted with high phytoconstituent concentration, manufactured under the same pharmaceutical-grade systems that define our allopathic portfolio.</p>
            <p>In <strong>2020</strong>, the next chapter began as <strong>Dhyey Soni</strong> — Hemang Soni's son and a B. Pharm and M. Finance graduate from <strong>IIT-Delhi</strong> — joined the family business, leading a new era of digital transformation, direct-to-consumer commerce, and modern formulation research grounded in classical Ayurvedic texts.</p>
            <p>Our guiding principle has remained unchanged across two generations: <em>"Extending Healthy Horizons"</em> — to every Indian family today, and to every corner of the globe tomorrow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-parent__links">
            <a href="https://www.prmpharmaceuticals.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--outline btn--small">
              Visit PRM Pharmaceuticals
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M7 17L17 7M7 7h10v10"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-parent__visual">
          <div class="about-parent__card">
            <div class="about-parent__card-head">
              <span class="about-parent__card-logo">PRM<span>Pharma</span></span>
              <span class="about-parent__card-year">Since 1999</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="about-parent__card-list">
              <li><strong>Allopathic</strong> — Core pharmaceutical manufacturing &amp; distribution</li>
              <li><strong>85+ Brands</strong> across therapy areas</li>
              <li><strong>250+ Formulations</strong> in tablets, syrups, capsules, ointments</li>
              <li><strong>28+ States, 3 Countries</strong> of active distribution</li>
              <li><strong>WHO-GMP, ISO 9001:2015</strong> certified facility</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="about-parent__card-divider"><span>Ayurvedic Division</span></div>
            <div class="about-parent__card-child">
              <span class="about-parent__card-logo about-parent__card-logo--child">Herbo<span>Villa</span></span>
              <span class="about-parent__card-year">Since 2013</span>
              <p>Classical Ayurvedic &amp; herbal formulations manufactured to pharmaceutical standards.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Ayurveda Philosophy — 3 Doshas {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-doshas section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-header__label">5,000 Years of Living Wisdom</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">The Philosophy of Ayurveda</h2>
        <p class="section-header__text">Ayurveda — <em>आयुर्वेद</em>, literally "the science of life" — sees every human as a unique balance of three <em>doshas</em>. Every HerboVilla formulation is composed with this balance in mind.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-doshas__grid">
        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--vata">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <path d="M6 20c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
              <path d="M6 28c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
              <path d="M6 36c8-6 14-2 20 0s14 2 16-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">वात</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Vata</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Air + Ether</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of movement — breath, circulation, thought, impulse. When balanced: creativity, vitality, clarity. When imbalanced: anxiety, dryness, insomnia.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Ashwagandha</span><span>Brahmi</span><span>Licorice</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--pitta">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <path d="M24 6c-6 8-10 14-10 22a10 10 0 0 0 20 0c0-8-4-14-10-22z"/>
              <path d="M20 28c0 4 2 6 4 6s4-2 4-6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">पित्त</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Pitta</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Fire + Water</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of transformation — metabolism, digestion, body heat, intellect. When balanced: sharp focus, strong digestion. When imbalanced: inflammation, acidity, irritability.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Amla</span><span>Neem</span><span>Triphala</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="dosha-card dosha-card--kapha">
          <div class="dosha-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
              <circle cx="24" cy="30" r="14"/>
              <path d="M24 16c0-6 4-10 4-10s4 4 4 10"/>
              <path d="M16 30c0-3 2-5 4-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="dosha-card__script">कफ</div>
          <h3 class="dosha-card__name">Kapha</h3>
          <p class="dosha-card__element">Earth + Water</p>
          <p class="dosha-card__text">The principle of structure — stability, lubrication, immunity, endurance. When balanced: calm, strength, resilience. When imbalanced: sluggishness, congestion, weight gain.</p>
          <div class="dosha-card__herbs">
            <span>Tulsi</span><span>Ginger</span><span>Turmeric</span>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <p class="about-doshas__footnote">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 2"/></svg>
        Most people are a dual dosha — a blend of two primary energies. Our wellness desk can help you understand your unique constitution.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Mission Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-mission section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-mission__grid">
        <div class="about-mission__image">
          {%- if section.settings.mission_image != blank -%}
            <img src="{{ section.settings.mission_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                 alt="{{ section.settings.mission_image.alt | default: 'Our Mission' }}"
                 loading="lazy">
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="about-mission__placeholder">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M40 10c-8 20-22 28-32 32 6 28 16 42 32 48 16-6 26-20 32-48-10-4-24-12-32-32z"/>
                <path d="M40 30v26M30 40h20M35 45c2 2 6 2 10 0M28 50h24"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="about-mission__content">
          <span class="about-mission__label">{{ section.settings.mission_label | default: 'Our Mission' }}</span>
          <h2 class="about-mission__title">{{ section.settings.mission_title | default: 'Bringing Ayurveda Home with Pharmaceutical Integrity' }}</h2>
          <div class="about-mission__text">
            {{ section.settings.mission_text | default: '<p>At HerboVilla, we believe Ayurveda deserves the same rigour as any modern medicine. Every formulation we produce is sourced from certified herbal suppliers, tested for heavy metals and microbial safety, and manufactured in a GMP-certified facility shared with our allopathic parent brand.</p><p>Our mission is simple: make authentic Ayurvedic wellness accessible to every Indian family — without compromise on purity, potency, or safety.</p>' }}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Values Section {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-values section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-header__label">{{ section.settings.values_label | default: 'What We Stand For' }}</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">{{ section.settings.values_title | default: 'Our Core Values' }}</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-values__grid">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'value' -%}
            <div class="value-card" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
              <div class="value-card__icon">
                {%- case block.settings.icon -%}
                  {%- when 'leaf' -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"/><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"/></svg>
                  {%- when 'shield' -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                  {%- when 'heart' -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
                  {%- when 'users' -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                  {%- when 'award' -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
                  {%- else -%}
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                {%- endcase -%}
              </div>
              <h3 class="value-card__title">{{ block.settings.title }}</h3>
              <p class="value-card__text">{{ block.settings.text }}</p>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} Story Timeline {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-story section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-header__label">{{ section.settings.story_label | default: 'Our Journey' }}</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">{{ section.settings.story_title | default: 'A Quarter Century of Building Trust' }}</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-timeline">
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">1999</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>PRM Pharmaceuticals is Founded</h3>
            <p>Mr. Hemang Soni founds PRM Pharmaceuticals in Bhavnagar, Gujarat as a first-generation pharmaceutical entrepreneur — built on the belief that quality Indian medicine should be accessible to every family. The very first product, <strong>Corylplus™</strong>, launches in the same year and becomes the cornerstone of the brand.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2005</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>National Distribution Footprint</h3>
            <p>Expansion across western and northern Indian states. Brand portfolio crosses 30+ formulations across antibiotics, anti-infectives, and chronic care therapy areas. PRM Pharma earns recognition as one of Gujarat's fastest-growing OTC pharmaceutical houses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2010</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>WHO-GMP Manufacturing Facility Commissioned</h3>
            <p>The Chitra G.I.D.C. plant in Bhavnagar (Plot 343/1-A) is commissioned — a WHO-GMP, Schedule T/M, and ISO 9001:2015 certified facility designed to global pharmaceutical standards for tablets, syrups, capsules, and topicals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item about-timeline__item--highlight">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2013</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>HerboVilla — The Ayurveda Division is Born</h3>
            <p>Responding to growing demand for authentic, safety-tested Ayurvedic medicines, PRM Pharma launches <strong>HerboVilla</strong> — a dedicated Ayurveda and herbal wellness brand, with a mission of <em>"SampurnaSudhha"</em> (Pure Quality), combining ancient Ayurveda with modern therapeutics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2018</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>AYUSH Licensed &amp; FSSAI Compliant</h3>
            <p>HerboVilla receives AYUSH Ministry licensing for both classical and proprietary Ayurvedic medicines, with parallel FSSAI compliance for nutraceutical formulations. Export footprint extends to 3 international markets.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item about-timeline__item--highlight">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2020</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>The Next Generation Joins</h3>
            <p><strong>Dhyey Soni</strong> — Hemang Soni's son and a B. Pharm and M. Finance graduate from <strong>IIT-Delhi</strong> — formally joins PRM Pharmaceuticals, leading the company's modernisation: digital transformation, direct-to-consumer commerce, and a new wave of formulation research grounded in classical Ayurvedic texts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2023</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>HerboVilla Goes Direct-to-Consumer</h3>
            <p>Launch of herbovilla.myshopify.com — the brand's first dedicated D2C channel, bringing HerboVilla's classical and proprietary formulations directly to Indian families without intermediaries.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-timeline__item">
          <div class="about-timeline__year">2024</div>
          <div class="about-timeline__body">
            <h3>35,000+ Customers · 300+ Distributors · 85+ Brands</h3>
            <p>Across 28+ Indian states and 3 international markets — 85+ brands, 250+ formulations, 35,000+ satisfied customers, and 300+ distributor channels. HerboVilla continues to be the fastest-growing division within the PRM group, faithful to a single tagline two generations strong: <em>Extending Healthy Horizons.</em></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

