          </div>
          <h3 class="sustain-card__title">Ethical Wildcrafting</h3>
          <p class="sustain-card__text">Forest-harvested herbs like Guggul and Shilajit sourced only from licensed cooperatives — never from threatened-species reserves.</p>
          <div class="sustain-card__stat"><strong>100%</strong> licensed suppliers</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sustain-card">
          <div class="sustain-card__icon sustain-card__icon--water">
