              <path d="M20 6c-6 8-10 14-10 20a10 10 0 0 0 20 0c0-6-4-12-10-20z"/>
              <path d="M14 28c0 2 2 4 4 4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="sustain-card__title">Water Stewardship</h3>
          <p class="sustain-card__text">Closed-loop water recycling at our Bhavnagar plant recovers &gt;85% of process water — critical in a water-stressed region of Gujarat.</p>
          <div class="sustain-card__stat"><strong>85%+</strong> water recycled</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sustain-card">
          <div class="sustain-card__icon sustain-card__icon--earth">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <rect x="6" y="12" width="28" height="20" rx="2"/>
              <path d="M12 12V8h16v4"/>
              <path d="M6 20h28"/>
              <circle cx="14" cy="26" r="2"/>
              <circle cx="26" cy="26" r="2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="sustain-card__title">Recyclable Packaging</h3>
          <p class="sustain-card__text">Amber-glass bottles and FSC-certified kraft cartons across our classical line — rolling out to 100% of the catalogue by 2026.</p>
          <div class="sustain-card__stat"><strong>2026</strong> full rollout</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sustain-card">
          <div class="sustain-card__icon sustain-card__icon--community">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="14" cy="16" r="4"/>
              <circle cx="26" cy="16" r="4"/>
              <circle cx="20" cy="28" r="4"/>
              <path d="M8 32c0-3 3-6 6-6M32 32c0-3-3-6-6-6"/>
              <path d="M14 34c0-3 3-6 6-6s6 3 6 6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="sustain-card__title">Farmer Partnerships</h3>
          <p class="sustain-card__text">Long-term buy-back agreements with 240+ contract farmers across four Indian states — fair prices, agronomy training, and guaranteed offtake.</p>
          <div class="sustain-card__stat"><strong>240+</strong> partner farmers</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sustain-card">
          <div class="sustain-card__icon sustain-card__icon--camp">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20 6l-14 28h28L20 6z"/>
              <path d="M20 20v14"/>
              <path d="M14 34l6-6 6 6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="sustain-card__title">Rural Health Camps</h3>
          <p class="sustain-card__text">Free Ayurvedic wellness camps in Bhavnagar &amp; Saurashtra villages — 30+ camps a year, run with BAMS doctors from our advisory panel.</p>
          <div class="sustain-card__stat"><strong>30+</strong> camps per year</div>
        </div>

        <div class="sustain-card">
          <div class="sustain-card__icon sustain-card__icon--solar">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="6"/>
              <path d="M20 4v4M20 32v4M4 20h4M32 20h4M8 8l3 3M29 29l3 3M8 32l3-3M29 11l3-3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
