  {%- comment -%} FAQ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-faq section section--alt">
    <div class="container about-faq__container">
      <div class="section-header section-header--center">
        <span class="section-header__label">Questions, Answered</span>
        <h2 class="section-header__title">Frequently Asked</h2>
        <p class="section-header__text">A few of the questions customers most often send our wellness desk. Can't find yours? Write to us — we respond within one business day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-faq__list">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Is HerboVilla the same company as PRM Pharmaceuticals?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>Yes. HerboVilla is the Ayurveda and herbal wellness division of PRM Pharmaceuticals, the parent pharmaceutical house founded in 1999. HerboVilla was launched in 2013, and every HerboVilla product is manufactured at the same Bhavnagar G.I.D.C. plant that produces PRM's allopathic portfolio.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Are your products safe for daily, long-term use?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>Our classical formulations are built on Ayurvedic compendia that have been in continuous use for centuries, and each batch is tested for heavy metals, pesticide residue, and microbial load against pharmacopoeia limits. That said, if you are pregnant, breastfeeding, on prescribed medication, or managing a chronic condition, please consult your physician or our wellness desk before beginning a new formulation.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Do you test for heavy metals and pesticides?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>Yes — on every production batch. Heavy metals (lead, mercury, cadmium, arsenic), pesticide residues, aflatoxins, and microbial load are screened in our QC lab against WHO-GMP and AYUSH pharmacopoeia limits before any batch is released.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Where are your herbs sourced from?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>From licensed organic farms and a network of 240+ contract farmers across Rajasthan, Kerala, Himachal Pradesh, and Gujarat. Forest-harvested herbs (Guggul, Shilajit) are sourced exclusively from licensed cooperatives. Every raw-material batch is identity-tested before acceptance.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Are HerboVilla products vegetarian?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>The large majority of our classical and proprietary formulations are vegetarian. A small number of classical formulations (e.g., Kasturi-containing or musk-based rasayanas) follow traditional recipes — these are labelled clearly on the pack and on the product page.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Do you ship pan-India? What about international orders?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>We currently ship to every serviceable PIN code in India, with most orders dispatched from Bhavnagar within 48 hours. International shipping is available on select SKUs — write to <a href="mailto:export@prmpharmaceuticals.com">export@prmpharmaceuticals.com</a> for country-specific documentation and pricing.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>Are you AYUSH licensed?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>Yes. HerboVilla holds AYUSH Ministry licensing for classical and proprietary Ayurvedic medicines, with parallel FSSAI approval for our nutraceutical SKUs. Our manufacturing facility is WHO-GMP and ISO 9001:2015 certified.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-item__q">
            <span>How do I know which product is right for me?</span>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-item__a">
            <p>Our wellness desk is staffed by BAMS-qualified Ayurvedic practitioners who can help you understand your prakriti (constitution) and match it to the right formulation. Book a free 15-minute call from our <a href="/pages/contact">Contact page</a> or start with our on-site prakriti quiz.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

